name: Circle Fly Free - Survive In The Orbit Circle
name_original: Circle Fly Free - Survive In The Orbit Circle
description:
Circle Fly is a game where the player must tap to fly and help the bird make it through the gaps. The hardest is that you do it while in Orbit! How long can you survive?

Features:
-Very Easy To Play
-Very Hard To Master
-Fits For All Ages
-Easy Graphics
-Techno Beat

This is the free version with a few ads - You can find the ad free version in the store.
